<br>
Pfff... now, play an enchanter : Would you prefer in your pickup groupe :<br>
A - A knight, where there is 95% chances (while playing as usual) than you will NOT a take one of those deadly double 500 or more in all your xp scession.<br>
B - A warrior, where there is 80% chances (while playing as usual) you WILL take a hit and maybe die if the warrior is not lucky with procs/taunt one time in all your xp scession.<br>
